{"tid":622921,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打玩過一隻陳年電單車game","createTime":"2018-04-09T14:06:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T18:24:44.000Z","uid":34241,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1f1b54b224a6c25390ec14f1296c96663a5e895d","tid":622921,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T14:06:42.000Z","msg":"首先大概係90年代既<br />\n買左隻KOF碟，但入面有個exe係模擬器<br />\n開左就有一堆小遊戲 (要load rom file)，metal slug, 賽車, mortal kombat都有<br />\n<br />\n有隻電單車game類似暴力摩托，<br />\n但無錶板，個背景無咁靚，<br />\n每個車手都可以出手/腳打人，<br />\n中左條友會慘叫<br />\n有D彎位會有灘水/油，高速踩過會跣軚<br />\n賽道一律黃泥色<br />\n有雙打模式，過左終點會泊橫部車對住鏡頭<br />\n<br />\n入game揀幾多cc既車，揀地圖，揀圈數<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打有印象 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"319b1b2be6bae283845d2121cb7c46ad1a272121","tid":622921,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T14:07:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/app/300380/Road_Redemption/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F300380%2FRoad_Redemption%2F&d=4dxi23YR79Ul%2FUsxr1StjsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=f9d690d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://store.steampowered.com/app/300380/Road_Redemption/</a>"},{"pid":"9f8716a60fd2b7469e9e8b24ee6007e78444e519","tid":622921,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"319b1b2be6bae283845d2121cb7c46ad1a272121","tid":622921,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T14:07:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/app/300380/Road_Redemption/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F300380%2FRoad_Redemption%2F&d=4dxi23YR79Ul%2FUsxr1StjsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=f9d690d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://store.steampowered.com/app/300380/Road_Redemption/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T14:09:36.000Z","msg":"用模擬器玩架喎<br />\n我估80-90年代出"},{"pid":"da49643ce2bce7de763b